{"tid":235213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（道德撚）澳男以蟹鉗代開啤酒，被全球批虐待動物","createTime":"2017-05-08T22:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T08:52:50.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65281910b7578d7a1d1a5087f39e8feabf73c3ca","tid":235213,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:30:31.000Z","msg":"【係咪虐待？】搵蟹鉗幫手開啤酒蓋 網民︰殺咗佢好過<br />\n<br />\n澳洲一名男子捉來一隻蟹，更把一瓶啤酒拿近牠，讓牠充當「開瓶器」開啤酒蓋；片段在社交網引起熱議，有人質疑男子虐待動物。<br />\n<br />\n標題為「皮爾巴拉（Pilbara、地方名）啤酒開瓶器」的片段上載至Facebook專頁，見到一名男子打開保溫箱，內裏有一隻蟹被困，男子將啤酒瓶伸至蟹鉗前方，讓蟹拑著瓶蓋，再順勢用力扭一扭，就成功開瓶。<br />\n有網民批評男子的行為不人道，「不要做混蛋，牠們遠離水源太久就不能生存」、「殺死牠或冰了牠」，不忍心看到蟹被玩弄。也有網民笑言︰「這隻蟹比我的狗狗有用。」<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170507/56661216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170507%2F56661216&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=312caf83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170507%2F56661216&h=2f7423a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170507/56661216</a><br />\n夾貓被批虐貓，夾龍蝦又無野<br />\n現在到拿蟹鉗開酒被批虐待了"},{"pid":"cfcbfce490ed43374cfe3de5a095b8b0249d99db","tid":235213,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:31:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dNx9tM_9sbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdNx9tM_9sbw&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b4d8b0ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dNx9tM_9sbw</a>"},{"pid":"8c7bae98cbee4afebaffceab3534b319dfa30b28","tid":235213,"uid":17081,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:51:16.000Z","msg":"個鉗壞咗呀~~~"},{"pid":"3da9df4cc573e7a725ef6f2f872fdbb836a0d3aa","tid":235213,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:53:20.000Z","ms